{"tid":1468174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"！我地所有曾經和平示威/夢遊既都見過身邊有疑似警察既假示威者！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:46:34.000Z","uid":2383,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36d9095685758af1012a681592257ad9b47a7f44","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"大家仔細咁回憶下自六月開始既每一次遊行，係咪都有見過類似警察既假示威者係身邊？<br />\n冇？<br />\n諗真D？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">佢地同811俾記者影到既差唔多<br />\n1.唔似普通人<br />\n2.體格強健<br />\n3.動作氣場夠冷靜有紀律<br />\n4.一時靠近其他人 一時又保持距離</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪有D印象？ 冇錯就係佢地<br />\n每次民陣遊行見到佢地<br />\n每次地區遊行（元朗、沙田、大角咀...）見到佢地<br />\n每一次帶頭衝擊警察好似都見到佢地蹤影<br />\n重點係 你唔係百分百肯定 不過你有見過類似氣場既人<br />\n佢地不斷出現係示威入面<br />\n疑似假扮示威者既警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由宜家起，你既回憶返返黎，記得好清楚，每次都硬係好似見過D類似既人，感覺好似警察既人<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不分化"},{"pid":"e3a38a5858443839f79a11bbe71983d592954799","tid":1468174,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNfTAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNfTAU.jpg&h=7becab2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9TyFfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9TyFfU.jpg&h=0b41b5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shGO9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shGO9f.jpg&h=e0856b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21d8d73247964ed586466b3da9966df298b28141","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"大家 係咪都見過？"},{"pid":"b8838284964a6d8dcc38d80a9cd07badc9c7f500","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:57.000Z","msg":"數量仲要好多"},{"pid":"94d362f1c2e40407c8f1284c7136208fa4c4a6e2","tid":1468174,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6190003db5da4e320fad47ad92ed9cec9ad3ee","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"點證明破壞交通燈既唔係扮示威者既警察"},{"pid":"d77565c097647468d0f0060eacebdcedbf0050b2","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"當聽到藍絲話示威者乜乜乜既時候<br />\n輕輕問返佢：你點知佢地係示威者抑或警察？"},{"pid":"972a918d3e66b32bf2ced8bc3bbd40164597a556","tid":1468174,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmCfTHY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmCfTHY.png&h=6af03681&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https: